{"tid":2080112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"議員轟警只准自己貼飾物","createTime":"2020-06-26T08:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T08:16:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f583c0c6d7e2fda8ece502de38f7114d06f5b6f5","tid":2080112,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200626/MVKTH6MQG6GLSVVRA3UYWL3LCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2FMVKTH6MQG6GLSVVRA3UYWL3LCU%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2hxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=c49b580a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2FMVKTH6MQG6GLSVVRA3UYWL3LCU%2F&h=f336ebe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200626/MVKTH6MQG6GLSVVRA3UYWL3LCU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n議員轟警只准自己貼飾物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fz1a_l6UQ3XG21Mqb1O4s_C5slU=/190x129/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IUQSRM4TFRZWPK3HLAGGAIG4I4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffz1a_l6UQ3XG21Mqb1O4s_C5slU%3D%2F190x129%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIUQSRM4TFRZWPK3HLAGGAIG4I4.jpg&h=1a061e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚文豪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方因不<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n要求紅十字會交名的舉動更是可疑。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：抽血員「反警」差佬拉隊走  要求交人不果 紅會致歉稱跟進<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n質疑「起人底」<br />\n<br />\n紅十字會曾到立<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n其實近日不少防暴警員均於制服貼上挑釁性標語，亦不見警方阻止。<br />\n<br />\n過往曾捐血的立法會議員涂謹申表示，按其個人經驗，無論填寫問卷還是抽血的過程中，不會特別留意抽血員的飾物。他又指若涉事抽血員的衣物上大字寫上「黑警死全家」，警員可視作合理冒犯，但若身上僅有細小飾物，警員即覺得不妥，恐是過份敏感，且包含政治審查。他又認為警員要求知道涉事抽血員的姓名，舉動更是可疑：「好怪，你想做乜嘢先？」<br />\n<br />\n政界人士亦對警方做法表示不滿，又一村區議員劉偉聰於fb說：「抽血員的飾物也得罪魔警。若要跪地求饒換魔警魔血，請紅十字會不要稀罕。」前立法會議員區諾軒則批評：「一班小氣到不堪，私怨大於公益的物體。」"},{"pid":"7236563a5c6ed36bca26fd50652704dab2f76c2a","tid":2080112,"uid":34289,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:16:07.000Z","msg":"民主派又贏 畫面好靚"}]}